com.edatasource.receipts.model.subscription

Interface AbstractSubscriptionReceipt.SubscriptionCategory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OnlineSubscription.EmailCategories, VideoRentalSubscription.VideoCategories
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractSubscriptionReceipt 

    public static interface AbstractSubscriptionReceipt.SubscriptionCategory
    The interface that concrete subscription classes must implement.

    This interface is used by the class to return the category name for that subscription type.

    In general, implementers will implement this interface with an inner-enum type. For an example, see the VideoRentalSubscription class
